text: Dubbel is a 2008 studio album by Lena Philipsson & Orup and part of their cooperation-project Lena + Orup. They have written the songs alone. The songs "Nu när du gått" and "Fem minuter i himmelen" charted at Svensktoppen, where they both stayed for three weeks, "Nu när du gått" between 26 OctoberSvensktoppen - 26 October 2008-9 November 2008Svensktoppen - 9 November 2008 and "Fem minuter i himmelen" between 15 Svensktoppen - 15 March 2009-29 March 2009.Svensktoppen - 29 March 2009 In 2010, the song "Fem minuter i himmelen" was recorded by Torgny Melins and Melissa Williams on the album Dansbandsnatt. ==Track listing== #"Hals över huvud" – 3:38 #"Nu när du gått" – 3:35 #"Fotbollsstjärna" – 2:47 #"Jag hatar att vakna utan dej" – 3:35 #"1 skäl" – 4:07 #"Fem minuter i himmelen" – 3:22 #"Bara en polis" – 3:45 #"Jag måste skynda mig på" – 4:00 #"Så mycket bättre än dom andra" – 3:59 #"Blott en skugga" – 2:39 ==Contributors== *Lena Philipsson — vocals *Orup — vocals, piano, keyboards, bass, guitar *Peter Månsson — keyboards, piano, organ, guitar, bass, programming, drums, percussion *Joakim Hemming — bass, guitar *Petter Bergander — piano, organ ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" ! scope="col"| Chart (2008-2009) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- ! scope="row"| Swedish Albums (Sverigetopplistan) | 2 |} == References == Category:2008 albums Category:Lena Philipsson albums Category:Orup albums
